      <title>国会坚持麦利的法令来支持新的IMF阿根廷交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/congress-upholds-milei-s-decree-to-back-new-imf-argentina-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷的下议院国会主席贾维尔·麦利（Javier Milei）的紧急执行法令支持与国际货币基金组织（International Intary Fund）的一项新协议，这是一个关键的立法步骤，为未来计划的详细信息宣布正式公告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/congress-upholds-milei-s-decree-to-back-new-imf-argentina-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 19:56:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税风险释放记录的铜运输量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/tariff-risk-unleashes-record-copper-shipments-bound-for-us-ports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国将被大量的铜一波淹没，作为全球在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）领先的领先关税的全球冲刺。]]></description>
